This paper deals with context modeling in robots, which is a core problem in robotics. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also uses a Recurrent Neural Network for learning, which falls under the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with machine learning and prediction, which are also covered in cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also uses scene modeling, which is a sub-topic of computer vision, falling under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with reasoning tasks, which is a sub-topic of control systems, falling under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
